$! Download forms and helpsheets for the past 4 tax years.$!

% The deadline for paper tax returns is 31 October. You have until 31 January if you send your return online. %

##2011 to 2012 tax year

Download the forms and helpsheets appropriate for your situation:

- [Individuals (including the self-employed) tax return (form SA100)](http://search2.hmrc.gov.uk/kb5/hmrc/forms/view.page?record=ZrJXAG2mt_0&formId=2999 "Self Assessment tax return (SA100) for individuals for the 2011 to 2012 tax year"){:rel="external"}  

- [Partnership tax return (form SA800)](http://search2.hmrc.gov.uk/kb5/hmrc/forms/view.page?record=LDtfIQn4taY&formId=3109 "Partnership tax return (SA800) for the 2011 to 2012 tax year"){:rel="external"}

- [Trust and estates tax return (form SA900)](http://search2.hmrc.gov.uk/kb5/hmrc/forms/selfassessmentforms.page#2050 "Trusts and Estates tax return (SA900) for the 2011 to 2012 tax year"){:rel="external"}

- [Non-resident companies tax return (form SA700)](http://search2.hmrc.gov.uk/kb5/hmrc/forms/view.page?record=BY1bV6sVDDA&formId=3146 "Non resident companies tax return (SA700) for the 2011 to 2012 tax year"){:rel="external"}

- [Trustees of registered pension schemes tax return (form SA970)](http://search2.hmrc.gov.uk/kb5/hmrc/forms/view.page?record=U2HGJsHggHg&formId=3148 "Trustees of registered pension schemes tax return (SA970) for the 2011 to 2012 tax year"){:rel="external"}

